{"id":"guide/i18n-common-overview","title":"Common Internationalization tasks","contents":"\n\n\n<div class=\"github-links\">\n  <a href=\"https://github.com/angular/angular-cn/edit/cn/aio/content/guide/i18n-common-overview.md?message=docs%3A%20请简述你的修改...\" aria-label=\"提供编辑建议\" title=\"提供编辑建议\"><i class=\"material-icons\" aria-hidden=\"true\" role=\"img\">mode_edit</i></a>\n</div>\n\n\n<div class=\"content\">\n  <h1 id=\"common-internationalization-tasks\" translation-result=\"on\">常见的国际化任务<a title=\"Link to this heading\" class=\"header-link\" aria-hidden=\"true\" href=\"guide/i18n-common-overview#common-internationalization-tasks\"><i class=\"material-icons\">link</i></a></h1><h1 translation-origin=\"off\">Common Internationalization tasks<a title=\"Link to this heading\" class=\"header-link\" aria-hidden=\"true\" href=\"guide/i18n-common-overview#common-internationalization-tasks\"><i class=\"material-icons\">link</i></a></h1>\n\n<p translation-result=\"on\">使用以下 Angular 任务来国际化你的项目。</p><p translation-origin=\"off\">Use the following Angular tasks to internationalize your project.</p>\n\n<ul>\n<li>\n<p translation-result=\"on\">使用内置管道以本地格式显示日期、数字、百分比和货币。</p><p translation-origin=\"off\">Use built-in pipes to display dates, numbers, percentages, and currencies in a local format.</p>\n\n</li>\n<li>\n<p translation-result=\"on\">在组件模板中标记文本以进行翻译。</p><p translation-origin=\"off\">Mark text in component templates for translation.</p>\n\n</li>\n<li>\n<p translation-result=\"on\">标记出要翻译的表达式的复数形式。</p><p translation-origin=\"off\">Mark plural forms of expressions for translation.</p>\n\n</li>\n<li>\n<p translation-result=\"on\">标记替代文本进行翻译。</p><p translation-origin=\"off\">Mark alternate text for translation.</p>\n\n</li>\n</ul>\n<p translation-result=\"on\">在为国际受众准备好项目之后，可以使用 <a href=\"cli\" title=\"CLI Overview and Command Reference | Angular\">Angular CLI</a> 来本地化你的项目。完成以下任务以本地化你的项目。</p><p translation-origin=\"off\">After you prepare your project for an international audience, use the <a href=\"cli\" title=\"CLI Overview and Command Reference | Angular\">Angular CLI</a> to localize your project.\nComplete the following tasks to localize your project.</p>\n\n<ul>\n<li>\n<p translation-result=\"on\">使用 CLI 将标记的文本提取到<em>源语言</em>文件中。</p><p translation-origin=\"off\">Use the CLI to extract marked text to a <em>source language</em> file.</p>\n\n</li>\n<li>\n<p translation-result=\"on\">为每种语言制作一份<em>源语言</em>文件的副本，并将所有<em>翻译</em>文件发送给翻译人员或翻译服务。</p><p translation-origin=\"off\">Make a copy of the <em>source language</em> file for each language, and send all of <em>translation</em> files to a translator or service.</p>\n\n</li>\n<li>\n<p translation-result=\"on\">在为一种或多种语言环境构建项目时，使用 CLI 合并已完成的翻译文件。</p><p translation-origin=\"off\">Use the CLI to merge the finished translation files when you build your project for one or more locales.</p>\n\n</li>\n</ul>\n<div class=\"alert is-helpful\">\n<p translation-result=\"on\">为所有目标语言环境创建一个强适应性的用户界面，将不同语言的间距等差异考虑在内。有关更多详细信息，请参阅<a href=\"https://marketfinder.thinkwithgoogle.com/intl/en_us/guide/how-to-approach-i18n#overview\" title=\"Overview - How to approach internationalization | Market Finder | Think with Google\">如何进行国际化</a>。</p><p translation-origin=\"off\">Create an adaptable user interface for all of your target locales that takes into consideration the differences in spacing for different languages.\nFor more details, see <a href=\"https://marketfinder.thinkwithgoogle.com/intl/en_us/guide/how-to-approach-i18n#overview\" title=\"Overview - How to approach internationalization | Market Finder | Think with Google\">How to approach internationalization</a>.</p>\n\n</div>\n<h2 id=\"prerequisites\" translation-result=\"on\">前提条件<a title=\"Link to this heading\" class=\"header-link\" aria-hidden=\"true\" href=\"guide/i18n-common-overview#prerequisites\"><i class=\"material-icons\">link</i></a></h2><h2 translation-origin=\"off\">Prerequisites<a title=\"Link to this heading\" class=\"header-link\" aria-hidden=\"true\" href=\"guide/i18n-common-overview#prerequisites\"><i class=\"material-icons\">link</i></a></h2>\n\n<p translation-result=\"on\">要准备翻译项目，你应该对以下主题有基本的了解。</p><p translation-origin=\"off\">To prepare your project for translations, you should have a basic understanding of the following subjects.</p>\n\n<ul>\n<li>\n<p translation-result=\"on\"><a href=\"guide/glossary#template\" title=\"template - Glossary | Angular\">模板</a></p><p translation-origin=\"off\"><a href=\"guide/glossary#template\" title=\"template - Glossary | Angular\">Templates</a></p>\n\n</li>\n<li>\n<p translation-result=\"on\"><a href=\"guide/glossary#component\" title=\"component - Glossary | Angular\">组件</a></p><p translation-origin=\"off\"><a href=\"guide/glossary#component\" title=\"component - Glossary | Angular\">Components</a></p>\n\n</li>\n<li>\n<p translation-result=\"on\"><a href=\"cli\" title=\"CLI Overview and Command Reference | Angular\">Angular CLI</a> <a href=\"guide/glossary#command-line-interface-cli\" title=\"command-line interface (CLI) - Glossary | Angular\">命令行</a>，管理 Angular 开发周期的工具</p><p translation-origin=\"off\"><a href=\"cli\" title=\"CLI Overview and Command Reference | Angular\">Angular CLI</a> <a href=\"guide/glossary#command-line-interface-cli\" title=\"command-line interface (CLI) - Glossary | Angular\">command-line</a> tool for managing the Angular development cycle</p>\n\n</li>\n<li>\n<p translation-result=\"on\"><a href=\"https://www.w3.org/XML\" title=\"Extensible Markup Language (XML) | W3C\">Extensible Markup Language (XML)</a> 用于翻译文件</p><p translation-origin=\"off\"><a href=\"https://www.w3.org/XML\" title=\"Extensible Markup Language (XML) | W3C\">Extensible Markup Language (XML)</a> used for translation files</p>\n\n</li>\n</ul>\n<h2 id=\"learn-about-common-angular-internationalization-tasks\" translation-result=\"on\">了解常见的 Angular 国际化任务<a title=\"Link to this heading\" class=\"header-link\" aria-hidden=\"true\" href=\"guide/i18n-common-overview#learn-about-common-angular-internationalization-tasks\"><i class=\"material-icons\">link</i></a></h2><h2 translation-origin=\"off\">Learn about common Angular internationalization tasks<a title=\"Link to this heading\" class=\"header-link\" aria-hidden=\"true\" href=\"guide/i18n-common-overview#learn-about-common-angular-internationalization-tasks\"><i class=\"material-icons\">link</i></a></h2>\n\n<div class=\"card-container\">\n    <a href=\"guide/i18n-common-add-package\" class=\"docs-card\" title=\"Add the localize package\">\n      <section ng-should-translate=\"\" translation-result=\"on\">添加 localize 包</section><section ng-should-translate=\"\" translation-origin=\"off\">Add the localize package</section>\n      \n      <p translation-result=\"on\">学习如何往项目中添加 Angular 的 localize 包</p><p translation-origin=\"off\">Learn how to add the Angular Localize package to your project</p>\n      \n      <p class=\"card-footer\" translation-result=\"on\">添加 localize 包</p><p class=\"card-footer\" translation-origin=\"off\">Add the localize package</p>\n      \n  </a>\n  <a href=\"guide/i18n-common-locale-id\" class=\"docs-card\" title=\"Refer to locales by ID\">\n    <section ng-should-translate=\"\" translation-result=\"on\">通过 ID 引用语言环境</section><section ng-should-translate=\"\" translation-origin=\"off\">Refer to locales by ID</section>\n    \n    <p translation-result=\"on\">学习如何标识语言环境标识符，并将其添加到项目</p><p translation-origin=\"off\">Learn how to identify and specify a locale identifier for your project</p>\n    \n    <p class=\"card-footer\" translation-result=\"on\">通过 ID 引用语言环境</p><p class=\"card-footer\" translation-origin=\"off\">Refer to locales by ID</p>\n    \n  </a>\n  <a href=\"guide/i18n-common-format-data-locale\" class=\"docs-card\" title=\"Format data based on locale\">\n    <section ng-should-translate=\"\" translation-result=\"on\">基于语言环境格式化数据</section><section ng-should-translate=\"\" translation-origin=\"off\">Format data based on locale</section>\n    \n    <p translation-result=\"on\">学习如何实现本地化数据管道，以及为项目改写默认语言环境</p><p translation-origin=\"off\">Learn how to implement localized data pipes and override the locale for your project</p>\n    \n    <p class=\"card-footer\" translation-result=\"on\">基于语言环境格式化数据</p><p class=\"card-footer\" translation-origin=\"off\">Format data based on locale</p>\n    \n  </a>\n  <a href=\"guide/i18n-common-prepare\" class=\"docs-card\" title=\"Prepare component for translation\">\n    <section ng-should-translate=\"\" translation-result=\"on\">准备翻译组件</section><section ng-should-translate=\"\" translation-origin=\"off\">Prepare component for translation</section>\n    \n    <p translation-result=\"on\">学习如何指定要翻译的源文本</p><p translation-origin=\"off\">Learn how to specify source text for translation</p>\n    \n    <p class=\"card-footer\" translation-result=\"on\">为翻译准备组件</p><p class=\"card-footer\" translation-origin=\"off\">Prepare component for translation</p>\n    \n  </a>\n  <a href=\"guide/i18n-common-translation-files\" class=\"docs-card\" title=\"Work with translation files\">\n    <section ng-should-translate=\"\" translation-result=\"on\">使用翻译文件</section><section ng-should-translate=\"\" translation-origin=\"off\">Work with translation files</section>\n    \n    <p translation-result=\"on\">学习如何检查和处理翻译文件</p><p translation-origin=\"off\">Learn how to review and process translation text</p>\n    \n    <p class=\"card-footer\" translation-result=\"on\">使用翻译文件</p><p class=\"card-footer\" translation-origin=\"off\">Work with translation files</p>\n    \n  </a>\n  <a href=\"guide/i18n-common-merge\" class=\"docs-card\" title=\"Merge translations into the application\">\n    <section ng-should-translate=\"\" translation-result=\"on\">把翻译结果合并回应用</section><section ng-should-translate=\"\" translation-origin=\"off\">Merge translations into the application</section>\n    \n    <p translation-result=\"on\">学习如何合并翻译结果，并构建翻译完的应用</p><p translation-origin=\"off\">Learn how to merge translations and build your translated application</p>\n    \n    <p class=\"card-footer\" translation-result=\"on\">把翻译结果合并回应用</p><p class=\"card-footer\" translation-origin=\"off\">Merge translations into the application</p>\n    \n  </a>\n  <a href=\"guide/i18n-common-deploy\" class=\"docs-card\" title=\"Deploy multiple locales\">\n    <section ng-should-translate=\"\" translation-result=\"on\">部署多个语言环境</section><section ng-should-translate=\"\" translation-origin=\"off\">Deploy multiple locales</section>\n    \n    <p translation-result=\"on\">学习如何为应用部署多个语言环境</p><p translation-origin=\"off\">Learn how to deploy multiple locales for your application</p>\n    \n    <p class=\"card-footer\" translation-result=\"on\">部署多个语言环境</p><p class=\"card-footer\" translation-origin=\"off\">Deploy multiple locales</p>\n    \n  </a>\n</div>\n<!-- links -->\n<!-- external links -->\n<!-- end links -->\n\n  <div class=\"reviewed\">最后复查时间： 10/7/2021</div>\n</div>\n\n\n<!-- links to this doc:\n - guide/i18n-overview\n-->\n<!-- links from this doc:\n - cli\n - guide/glossary#command-line-interface-cli\n - guide/glossary#component\n - guide/glossary#template\n - guide/i18n-common-add-package\n - guide/i18n-common-deploy\n - guide/i18n-common-format-data-locale\n - guide/i18n-common-locale-id\n - guide/i18n-common-merge\n - guide/i18n-common-overview#common-internationalization-tasks\n - guide/i18n-common-overview#learn-about-common-angular-internationalization-tasks\n - guide/i18n-common-overview#prerequisites\n - guide/i18n-common-overview#了解常见的-angular-国际化任务\n - guide/i18n-common-overview#前提条件\n - guide/i18n-common-overview#常见的国际化任务\n - guide/i18n-common-prepare\n - guide/i18n-common-translation-files\n - https://github.com/angular/angular-cn/edit/cn/aio/content/guide/i18n-common-overview.md?message=docs%3A%20请简述你的修改...\n - https://marketfinder.thinkwithgoogle.com/intl/en_us/guide/how-to-approach-i18n#overview\n - https://www.w3.org/XML\n-->"}